</p>

<p>
The way in which alone this difficult problem can be solved we shall examin=
e in
the book on the =E2=80=9CTheory of War.=E2=80=9D In every case the concepti=
on of
War, as here defined, will be the first ray of light which shows us the tru=
e
foundation of theory, and which first separates the great masses and allows=
 us
to distinguish them from one another.
</p>

