<p>
The one part belongs, in one respect, to the combat itself, is identical wi=
th
it, whilst it serves in another respect for the maintenance of the military
force. The other part belongs purely to the subsistence, and has only, in
consequence of the reciprocal action, a limited influence on the combats by=
