<div class=3D"chapter">

<h3><a name=3D"chap21"></a>CHAPTER VII.<br>Perseverance</h3>

<p>
The reader expects to hear of angles and lines, and finds, instead of these
citizens of the scientific world, only people out of common life, such as h=
e
meets with every day in the street. And yet the author cannot make up his m=
ind
to become a hair=E2=80=99s breadth more mathematical than the subject seems=
 to
him to require, and he is not alarmed at the surprise which the reader may
