different according to the means and end.
</p>

<p>
It seems incredible, and yet it has happened a hundred times, that troops h=
ave
been divided and separated merely through a mysterious feeling of conventio=
nal
manner, without any clear perception of the reason.
</p>

<p>
If the concentration of the whole force is acknowledged as the norm, and ev=
ery
