re
general their destination.
</p>

<p>
The point where the idea of a strategic reserve begins to become inconsiste=
nt
is not difficult to determine: it lies in the SUPREME DECISION. Employment =
must
be given to all the forces within the space of the supreme decision, and ev=
ery
reserve (active force available) which is only intended for use after that
