</p>

<p>
If there is a suspension of action in War, that is, if neither party wills
something positive, there is rest, and consequently equilibrium, but certai=
nly
an equilibrium in the largest signification, in which not only the moral an=
d
physical war-forces, but all relations and interests, come into calculation=
