</p>

<p class=3D"footnote">
(*) October 14, 1758.
</p>

<p>
In recent times, when War has been carried on with so much more rapidity an=
d
vigour, it has in consequence often happened that Armies have encamped very
close to each other, without having a very strong system of outposts, becau=
se
