r by
other causes.
</p>

<p>
Austria and Russia are states which have kept up a numerous cavalry, becaus=
e
they retain in their political condition the fragments of a Tartar
organisation. Buonaparte for his purposes could never be strong enough in
cavalry; when he had made use of the conscription as far as possible, he ha=
