<p>
Lastly, in winter quarters, the rigour of the season may also be a reason f=
or
breaking up the advanced guard into a line of posts, because it is easier t=
o
find shelter for it in that way.
</p>

<p>
The use of a reinforced line of outposts was brought to great perfection by=
