</p>

<p>
Of course this is a mere rough estimate of what may take place, subject to =
many
modifying circumstances which may intervene, of which the principal is, tha=
t
one district may not be capable of contributing like another. But on the ot=
her
hand, we must also remember that the radius within which we can levy may
