</p>

<p>
The consequence is that all deductions from the length of the base of
operations and its angles, and the whole theory of war founded on these dat=
a,
as far as its geometrical phase, have never met with any attention in real =
war,
and in theory they have only caused wrong tendencies. But as the basis of t=
his
chain of reasoning is a truth, and only the conclusions drawn are false, th=
is
