that the whole course of the battle will be changed by the successful charg=
e of
a few battalions or squadrons. His position is <i>deep</i>, for each part i=
n
the scale of gradation of the order of battle, from the division down to th=
e
battalion, has its reserve for unforeseen events, and for a renewal of the
