</p>

<p>
We have not yet noticed the frontiers of the state, nor said anything of th=
e
geometrical form of the whole system of fortresses, nor of the other
geographical points in connection with their situation, because we regard t=
he
objects above mentioned as the most essential, and are of opinion that in m=
any
cases they alone are sufficient, particularly in small states. But, at the =
same
