considered whether it would not be better, in place of Nuremburg, to fortif=
y
some other place in the neighbourhood of Munich, even if the place is one o=
f
less importance in itself.
</p>

<p>
As concerns the decision in such cases, that is, answering the first questi=
on,
we must refer to what has been said in the chapters on the general plan of
