<p>
We have, therefore, now ascertained that=E2=80=94
</p>

<p>
1. A considerable length,
</p>

<p>
2. An oblique direction,
</p>

<p>
3. An enemy=E2=80=99s province,
</p>

<p>
are the principal circumstances under which the lines of communication of a=
n
