<h3><a name=3D"chap91"></a>CHAPTER XXVI.<br>Arming the Nation</h3>

<p>
A people=E2=80=99s war in civilised Europe is a phenomenon of the nineteent=
h
century. It has its advocates and its opponents: the latter either consider=
