<div class=3D"chapter">

<h3><a name=3D"chap100"></a>CHAPTER V.<br>Culminating Point of the Attack</=
h3>

<p>
The success of the attack is the result of a present superiority of force, =
it
being understood that the moral as well as physical forces are included. In=
