<div class=3D"chapter">

<h3><a name=3D"chap101"></a>CHAPTER VI.<br>Destruction of the Enemy=E2=80=
=99s Armies</h3>

<p>
The destruction of the enemy=E2=80=99s armed forces is the means to the
end=E2=80=94What is meant by this=E2=80=94The price it costs=E2=80=94Differ=
